

			scull - character device
			
		scull porting to 4.15.0-33-generic kernel.

	Attempt to port scull driver and make it fully functional
	on the new kernel distribution. Based on the 2005's book 
	Linux Device Drivers by Corbet,Rubini and Hartman.Changes
	introduced in scripts and on deprecated functions as well
	in the context of improving functionality. 
				
	Documentation for the 'scull' driver.
	
	@Re-written by Mouzakitis Nikolaos 2018.


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|										|
| scull.c	:		module's code.					|
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|										|
| scull_load.sh : 	load the module into the Kernel and create		|
|			the appropriate files in the /dev.			|
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|										|
| scull_unload.sh:	unloads module from kernel as well as deleting		|
|			entries of device in /dev.				|
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
